    "C. Results and DiscussionTable II summarizes the performance of each LLM across different API modules and function classifications.",
    "The results indicate that GPT-4 achieves the highest performance across both metrics, with an overall MLC-Acc of 0.992 and an average FLC-Acc of 0.996.",
